  <p>When we tell tradesmen about our <a href="/ai-receptionist-for-tradesmen">AI receptionist</a>, the first question is always the same: <strong>"Is it actually as good as a real person?"</strong></p>

  <p>Fair question. Let's compare them honestly — cost, availability, consistency, and actual results — and let you decide.</p>

  <h2>Cost Comparison</h2>

  <p>Let's start with the number everyone cares about.</p>

